# ===== Shoprunback (Office 365, XOAUTH2 via oama) =====
IMAPAccount shoprunback
Host outlook.office365.com
Port 993
User vanny@shoprunback.com
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
PassCmd "oama access vanny@shoprunback.com"
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.2 +1.3

IMAPStore shoprunback-remote
Account shoprunback

MaildirStore shoprunback-local
Path ~/.mail/shoprunback/
Inbox ~/.mail/shoprunback/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel shoprunback
Far :shoprunback-remote:
Near :shoprunback-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Sent Items" "Drafts" "Deleted Items" "Junk Email" "Archive"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# ===== Gmail (app password via pass) =====
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User kongvanny2000@gmail.com
AuthMechs LOGIN
PassCmd "pass show personal/gmail/kongvanny2000@gmail.com/app_passwords/aerc"
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.2 +1.3

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Bin" "[Gmail]/Spam" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
